Author: happybumblebree
Text: i feel it dude.   but also you deserve a meal, even an unhealthy one. there are a lot of opportunities to fast, it's okay to break one for the sake of friendship and, you know, life outside of ED.

Author: notracisthasblackcat
Text: When you look back on this, hopefully you will remember enjoying a great meal with a friend and not the feeling of bloat or shame. We have to live once in a while :)
